{"tid":2327640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★政府公布最新長策目標　未來10年供應43萬伙","createTime":"2020-12-16T08:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T11:20:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6b14e9f2bef571f05bc0be7729af883ec552b3f5","tid":2327640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"政府在施政報告公布，首次達到《長遠房屋策略》覓得330公頃土地的目標。新一份《長策》周年進度報告推算，2021/22至2030/31年度10年總房屋供應目標介乎40.5萬與45.1萬伙之間，中間數為42.8萬伙，較去年推算的中位數為42.5萬伙多3000伙。但經當局四捨五入計算後，10年總房屋供應目標為43萬伙，與去年所訂立的目標相同。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/562420/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E9%95%B7%E7%AD%96%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%8610%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%8943%E8%90%AC%E4%BC%99-%E5%85%AC%E7%87%9F%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E9%A6%96%E9%81%94%E6%A8%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F562420%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25AD%2596%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%25A8%2599-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%258610%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%258943%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BC%2599-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%2587%259F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%25A8%2599&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMUx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=b782553d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/562420/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E9%95%B7%E7%AD%96%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%8610%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%8943%E8%90%AC%E4%BC%99-%E5%85%AC%E7%87%9F%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E9%A6%96%E9%81%94%E6%A8%99</a>"},{"pid":"c397d911100f554068f47b99ffe1f5a73f1d9b73","tid":2327640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1006714ef7e6a9fef508aa0f0b26920a44bb414c","tid":2327640,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"8萬5政策？董建華落台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5331bedcf2b2d034b45ec09cac9d10e49706450d","tid":2327640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">未來5年可供應10.1萬伙公營房屋</span><br />\n<br />\n當局沿用2018年調整公私營房屋供應的70:30比例，當中30.1萬個公營房屋供應中，「公屋/ 綠置居」單位佔21萬個，其餘的9.1萬個則為「其他資助出售單位」。截至今年9月，在2020/21至2024/25年度的5年期內，香港房屋委員會和香港房屋協會的公營房屋預計總建屋量為10.1萬個單位，包括7.05萬個公屋/綠置居和3.08萬個其他資助出售單位，合共較去年推算的5年期多4000個單位。<br />\n<br />\n政府在新一份《施政報告》中提到，已覓得330公頃土地興建31.6萬個公營房屋單位，較上一個10年期多4.4萬伙。31.6萬個單位中，主要來自新發展區項目、棕地群、收回部份粉嶺高球場等，預計約三分一會在第一個5年落成，當中大部分已完成諮詢、法定改劃等程序，當局形容有關項目的落成時間較確實；其餘的三分之二則會在第2個5年期落成，大部分土地亦已改劃用途，正待收地、清拆和重置等程序。但陳帆亦強調，上述工作有可能因不同原因而「拖延」。<br />\n<br />\n至於私營房屋方面，當局預料未來3至4年，一手私人住宅物業市場的供應量約為9.2萬伙。"},{"pid":"11bee3fec4595740d0df58210d88ee4f6a6bf21c","tid":2327640,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"人類總是重複犯錯"},{"pid":"97253e843a5403cfe0ca2d97426c69c05af2498c","tid":2327640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"blue<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjavV64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjavV64.jpg&h=6e12c3fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b10327bb06e35ad88f1613f6a8d7c462a97a7e86","tid":2327640,"uid":33352,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"計劃同建議姐，有邊年係起夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔夠數咪出嚟道歉同會改善下，之後咪一樣唔夠<br />\n<br />\n咪當人唔識嫁大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9e78d9369a51bf0569f890c5c13ac8c6386e87","tid":2327640,"uid":50502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"收地起公屋居屋 擺明比廢老新移民住<br />\n唔起私樓 等你班成世月入兩萬令既廢青大學生繼續儲錢買私人市場 <br />\n樓價繼續gogogo"},{"pid":"9b02c9ef9a0360616511f5b355afd5174d851388","tid":2327640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1006714ef7e6a9fef508aa0f0b26920a44bb414c","tid":2327640,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"8萬5政策？董建華落台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:16:54.000Z","msg":"就咁9up下，d收成期藍絲 已經發曬癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28e449763b3fe9d7b3085060879c7a1f562c006","tid":2327640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3b9e78d9369a51bf0569f890c5c13ac8c6386e87","tid":2327640,"uid":50502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"收地起公屋居屋 擺明比廢老新移民住<br />\n唔起私樓 等你班成世月入兩萬令既廢青大學生繼續儲錢買私人市場 <br />\n樓價繼續gogogo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:17:23.000Z","msg":"又話移民？"},{"pid":"1221821c716e828f0c6771f8adf63d10470762f4","tid":2327640,"uid":238415,"like":1,"d